The paper discusses the development and use of chatbots in human-computer communication, which falls under the category of natural language processing and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of techniques such as machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in chatbot development. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential applications of chatbots in human-computer interaction and user interfaces (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the use of large-scale corpora (cs.IR) and the coupling of chatbot development with current research in the field (cs.LG).
